channel.title: Errors after Compling
channel.description:
When i compile i get 14 errors src\server\model\players\packets\Commands.java:19: error: duplicate class: serve r.model.players.packets.Commands public class Commands implements PacketType ^ src\server\model\players\Commands.java:974: error: cannot find symbol c.hail(); ^ symbol: method hail() location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\Commands.java:977: error: cannot find symbol c.barrage(); ^ symbol: method barrage() location: variable c of type Client src\server\model\players\Commands.java:980: error: cannot find symbol c.zombie(); ^ symbol: method zombie() location: variable c of type Client Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 4 errors
I tried putting some commands in, didnt work so i put my backup in, there shouldnt be errors since its the backup that works, but i get them errors, Anyone know what todo? Thanks if you can
